{"tid":2355562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請珍惜連登","createTime":"2021-01-06T07:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T08:02:24.000Z","uid":37396,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a83b3279e12097246472fba924a1c70d6920c66","tid":2355562,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"見倒今日嘅新聞<br />\n越嚟越覺得連登好快會比港共搞<br />\n我甚至覺得捱唔倒今年<br />\n<br />\n連登作為反送中運動最大平台<br />\n可以話係香港網絡上僅餘最可以暢所欲言嘅論壇<br />\n你可以話今時今日連登已經比五毛/PR 佔據<br />\n但你唔可以否認暫時呢一刻你仲可以喺連登講乜都得<br />\n而好明顯呢啲日子好快就會完<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望各位連登仔珍惜唔知仲有幾耐嘅自由<br />\n停止再鬥黃<br />\n時間真係無多<br />\n可以嘅話一齊諗下仲可以用呢個平台做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n黎明前嘅黑暗係至撚黑暗<br />\n但我想講而家只係黑暗嘅開始<br />\n我真係唔知下一年嘅今日仲可唔可以喺度講野<br />\n<br />\n連仔如果睇倒呢個POST<br />\n希望你地真係要做定心理準備<br />\n最重要係確保所有會員嘅資料唔會比黑警拎倒<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">請珍惜連登</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bd915e928207dfa915fca33aeb69a6ad31ca9c","tid":2355562,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f59cc7eb66dd6ac8e69509c612a81c0280f23e","tid":2355562,"uid":258429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,